org.cougaar.mts.base
Interface ReceiveLink

All Known Implementing Classes:
ReceiveLinkDelegateImplBase, ReceiveLinkImpl, TraceAspect.ReceiveLinkDelegate
public interface ReceiveLink

The final station in the message transport system before an incoming message is delivered to an Agent. One ReceiveLink is instantiated for each MessageTransportClient.

The previous station is MessageDeliverer.

See Also:
MessageTransportService.registerClient(MessageTransportClient), SendLink, SendQueue, Router, DestinationQueue, DestinationLink, MessageWriter, MessageReader, Javadoc contributions from George Mount.
